items.name: Robopedia
items.title: Robopedia
items.headline: Check out the Custom Robo Wikia!
items.desc: Custom Robo is an action-fighting game franchise developed by NOISE and published by Nintendo. There currently are five iterations in the series, but only the last two, Custom Robo and Custom Robo Arena, have been released in America and Europe. The bulk of gameplay takes place within holosseums where two miniature robots battle it out with various guns, bombs, and pods. Success is based on how well the robo is controlled, but more importantly, how it was customized.

items.name: Mr. Men Wiki
items.title: Mr. Men Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Mr. Men Wiki!
items.desc: Mr. Men is a series of 49 children's books by Roger Hargreaves commencing in 1971. The series features characters with names such as Mr. Tickle and Mr. Happy who have personalities and physical attributes based on their names. After Hargreaves's death in 1988, his son Adam Hargreaves began writing and illustrating new stories, including four characters that his father had developed before his death.

items.title: Mr. Bean Wiki
items.headline: All about Rowan Atkinson's Mr. Bean
items.desc: Mr. Bean is a British comedy television show about a silly buffoon with the same name. Mr. Bean has been very popular on TV and has been played by Rowan Atkinson. He had later gotten a movie based on the show as the star and soon an animated series. While the series may be over now, we can still try and show our love for it here at the Mr. Bean Wiki.

items.name: Maximum Ride Wiki
items.title: Maximum Ride Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Maximum Ride Wiki!
items.desc: The Maximum Ride Wiki is a collaborative online project dedicated to providing accurate and detailed information about American author James Patterson's bestselling Maximum Ride novel series. Founded in 2009, the Maximum Ride Wiki covers both in-universe topics - such as characters and locations - and real-world topics - such as authors and adaptations; and because of the site's structure and format, even you can help us expand it!

items.name: Mr young Wiki
items.title: Mr young Wiki
items.headline: Learn More about Mr. Young Wikia!
items.desc: The Mr. Young Wikia is a community site dedicated to the Mr. Young Canadian comedy TV series. This highschool sitcom lasted from 2011 to 2013. If you are a fan of this series, just curious about it, or a fan of high-school sitcoms then this is the place for you! We would like the old fans to come back. At the moment, this wikia doesn't have web traffic, so we are hoping through this advertisement to gain some web traffic. Although it might be a stretch because the show's buzz has died down from its cancellation, we can always try. If you are new to this show, access might be limited on the web. However, you are welcome to watch it on Youtube for most episodes, watch on Netflix, or purchase the series volumes on the Apple Store. Please come and explore our content and help us maybe to expand this database... or join us in discussion about the characters, the episodes, or the series in general. Thanks for reading this ad!
